Classification Model
Developed binary classifier to distinguish spam vs. ham emails
Engineered custom text features using regex and tokenization
Implemented logistic regression model with precision/recall evaluation
Optimized classification threshold to improve F1 score 

Prediction Model
Built end-to-end regression pipeline in Python to predict housing prices using feature engineering and log transformations
Implemented OLS, regularization techniques, and cross-validation
Performed outlier detection and data cleaning to improve model robustness
Evaluated model performance using RMSE and R² metrics
